         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* This macro replaces the assembler's USING statement                  00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   USING &DSECT,                 * Control block name            *00200000
               &BASE                   * Register (or field) for using  00210000
.*                                                                      00220000
.* &LABEL optional USING label                                          00230000
.* &DSECT specifies the control block to be set addressable.            00240000
.* &BASE  specifies either a register that points to &DSECT or a field  00250000
.*        that contains a &DSECT as a label. If specified as a register 00260000
.*        other registers may follow.                                   00270000
.*                                                                      00280000
.********************************************************************** 00281001
.*                                                                      00282001
